        <p>You can minimize the ribbons so that you only see the top portion of the ribbons until you select an option. To do this, right-click anywhere in a ribbon and select <span class="Emphasis">Minimize the Ribbon</span> from the context menu. See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Interface/Customizing_the_Workspace/Minimizing_Ribbons.htm" target="" title="" alt="">Minimizing Ribbons</MadCap:xref>.</p>
